</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Fitness Plan (26-40 Underweight)</h1>
        
        <h2>Diet Plan (Weekly Variation)</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Breakfast</th>
                <th>Lunch</th>
                <th>Snacks</th>
                <th>Dinner</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Scrambled eggs with avocado toast and a fruit smoothie</td>
                <td>Grilled chicken with quinoa and steamed vegetables</td>
                <td>Nuts, dried fruits, and a protein shake</td>
                <td>Baked salmon with sweet potatoes and sautéed spinach</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Oatmeal with peanut butter, banana, and honey</td>
                <td>Lean beef stir-fry with brown rice</td>
                <td>Greek yogurt with granola and mixed nuts</td>
                <td>Grilled tofu with whole wheat pasta and roasted veggies</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Whole wheat pancakes with almond butter and berries</td>
                <td>Grilled fish with mashed potatoes and green beans</td>
                <td>Boiled eggs and a banana</td>
                <td>Chicken curry with basmati rice and steamed carrots</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Protein smoothie (milk, oats, peanut butter, banana, protein powder)</td>
                <td>Grilled shrimp with quinoa and stir-fried bell peppers</td>
                <td>Cheese cubes with almonds</td>
                <td>Lentil soup with whole grain bread</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Omelet with cheese, mushrooms, and whole wheat toast</td>
                <td>Chicken wrap with hummus and salad</td>
                <td>Avocado toast with sunflower seeds</td>
                <td>Baked turkey breast with roasted sweet potatoes</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>French toast with maple syrup and walnuts</td>
                <td>Grilled tofu with wild rice and sautéed greens</td>
                <td>Dark chocolate and mixed dried fruits</td>
                <td>Beef stew with brown rice and a side of steamed broccoli</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Chia pudding with nuts and honey</td>
                <td>Salmon salad with avocado and quinoa</td>
                <td>Cashews and a protein bar</td>
                <td>Vegetable stir-fry with tofu and whole grain noodles</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <h2>Gym Routine (Balanced Plan)</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Workout</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Full-body strength training (Squats, Deadlifts, Bench Press)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Low-intensity cardio (brisk walking) + Core workout</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Upper body strength (Pull-ups, Shoulder Press, Dumbbell Rows)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Rest & Recovery (Stretching, Yoga, Foam rolling)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Lower body strength (Deadlifts, Lunges, Leg Press)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Outdoor Activity (Hiking, Swimming, Cycling)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Rest & Recovery</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
